description: Go ahead and ask Alexa for a flat earth fact and she can now tell you or your doubting friends about the true shape of the world.  Don't take NASA's word for it.  None of their pictures or videos are real and they admit that.  Find truth here.

Alexa start Flat Earth Facts and give me a fact
name: FlatEarthFacts
shortDescription: Offers some insight into the shape of the world by giving you a random flat earth fact.
